beer.beer_description:
Aromatic coﬀee from Kaﬃbrennsla Akureyrar 
subtly bands together with toasted malt undertones in our Baltic Porter. While dark in 
color, this classical version of a lagered porter has a medium mouthfeel and dark chocolate notes that 
result in a smooth on the palate, easy-to-drink 
brew you'll want to face again and again.
